CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781302284
OL,3,CUS and Iran exchange strikes for
OL,4,Csecond night in a row
OL,6,FThe United States launched a second
OL,7,Fround of airstrikes on Iran overnight
OL,8,Finto Thursday, with Iran responding by
OL,9,Fstriking targets in Bahrain, Kuwait
OL,10,Fand Jordan.
OL,12,FIt comes after US President Donald
OL,13,FTrump warned Tehran that it would "pay
OL,14,Fthe price" over a lack of progress in
OL,15,Freaching a peace deal.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781302284
OL,3,CUS and Iran exchange strikes for
OL,4,Csecond night in a row
OL,6,FWith efforts to negotiate an end to
OL,7,Fthe war appearing stuck, Iran insisted
OL,8,Fit would maintain its chokehold on the
OL,9,FStrait of Hormuz, which has disrupted
OL,10,Fglobal energy supplies and pushed up
OL,11,Foil prices.
OL,13,FThe ensuing American attack across
OL,14,Fmultiple Iranian cities appeared more
OL,15,Fintense than the day before, although
OL,16,Fthe Tehran government released no
OL,17,Finformation about what was hit.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781302284
OL,3,CUS and Iran exchange strikes for
OL,4,Csecond night in a row
OL,6,FKuwait, one of Washington's allies in
OL,7,Fthe Gulf region, closed its airspace
OL,8,Fbecause of the Thursday morning
OL,9,Fattack, without elaborating on any
OL,10,Fdamage.
OL,12,FJordan didn't acknowledge the attack,
OL,13,Fthough the US Embassy in Amman warned
OL,14,Fabout it. Bahrain sounded its missile
OL,15,Falert sirens without mentioning
OL,16,Fpossible damage there.
OL,18,FThe US Central Command said its latest
OL,19,Fround of airstrikes ended just before
OL,20,Fsunrise on Thursday in Iran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781302284
OL,3,CUS and Iran exchange strikes for
OL,4,Csecond night in a row
OL,6,FIt said the strikes were "in response
OL,7,Fto Iran's unwarranted and continued
OL,8,Faggression" and targeted "Iranian
OL,9,Fmilitary surveillance capabilities,
OL,10,Fcommunication systems and air defence
OL,11,Fsites".
OL,13,FExplosions from the strikes echoed
OL,14,Faround Iran's capital, Tehran, as well
OL,15,Fas the port city of Bandar Abbas and
OL,16,Fother southern areas along the Strait
OL,17,Fof Hormuz.
OL,26,@nD@ZOUpD@KO]pD@ZOUsD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781302284
OL,3,CUS and Iran exchange strikes for
OL,4,Csecond night in a row
OL,6,FEarly on Thursday, Israel also warned
OL,7,Fresidents in the north to seek shelter
OL,8,Fafter the detection of suspected
OL,9,Fincoming fire from Lebanon.
OL,11,FThe third back-and-forth strikes this
OL,12,Fweek puts in jeopardy an already shaky
OL,13,Ftwo-month ceasefire still notionally
OL,14,Fin place.
OL,16,FThe first were attacks between Iran
OL,17,Fand Israel on Sunday into Monday,
OL,18,Ffollowed by the two rounds of fire
OL,19,Fbetween America and Tehran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781302284
OL,3,CUS and Iran exchange strikes for
OL,4,Csecond night in a row
OL,6,FTrump has urged Iran to sign a deal to
OL,7,Fend the war and suggested earlier this
OL,8,Fweek that an agreement could be
OL,9,Freached in days.
OL,11,FBut Iran has proved resilient despite
OL,12,Fweeks of heavy bombing, and its
OL,13,Fability to effectively close the
OL,14,FStrait of Hormuz ` a crucial
OL,15,Fpassageway for oil and natural gas `
OL,16,Fgives it a strong bargaining chip.
OL,18,FStill, both countries seem to be
OL,19,Flooking for a way to end the conflict
OL,20,F`if they can manage to sell it as a
OL,21,Fwin at home.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781302284
OL,3,CUS and Iran exchange strikes for
OL,4,Csecond night in a row
OL,6,FTrump said that since last month, the
OL,7,FUS military has undertaken a "secret
OL,8,Fmission" to sneak oil shipments past
OL,9,FIran's forces in the Strait of Hormuz.
OL,11,FHe said ships were slipping through at
OL,12,Fnight, aided by the destruction of
OL,13,FIranian radar equipment, resulting in
OL,14,F100 million barrels of oil evading
OL,15,FIran's chokehold of the strait.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
