PN,31908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781302284
OL,3,CUS and Iran exchange strikes for
OL,4,Csecond night in a row
OL,6,FThere was no immediate confirmation of
OL,7,Fthat figure, which roughly equals five
OL,8,Fdays of oil shipments through the
OL,9,Fwaterway before the war began. The
OL,10,Fmilitary's role was not immediately
OL,11,Fclear.
