FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781302284
OL,3,CUS and Iran exchange strikes for
OL,4,Csecond night in a row
OL,6,FWary of high petrol prices in the run-
OL,7,Fup to midterm elections in November,
OL,8,FTrump seems to be looking for a quick
OL,9,Fwin, but he is also making demands
OL,10,Fthat will be tough for Iran to swallow.
OL,12,FThe US wants to see Iran give up its
OL,13,Fstockpile of highly enriched uranium.
OL,14,FWhile Iran insists its nuclear program
OL,15,Fis peaceful, that uranium is a short
OL,16,Ftechnical step from weapons-grade
OL,17,Flevels.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781302284
OL,3,CUS and Iran exchange strikes for
OL,4,Csecond night in a row
OL,6,FIran is refusing to give up the
OL,7,Furanium and demanding relief from
OL,8,Fsanctions. It also wants the release
OL,9,Fof frozen assets even before a final
OL,10,Fagreement is in place, something Trump
OL,11,Frejected.
OL,13,FIran has insisted that any deal to end
OL,14,Fthe war must also end fighting between
OL,15,Fits ally Hezbollah and Israel.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
